          Heading link



 
Copy link








Research 
Home to leading journals in the field, including New Media and Society, Social Media and Society, and  Mobile Media in Communication.







Curriculum 
Recently ranked in the top 50 worldwide, Communication@UIC  offers a BA, MA and PhD with emphasis on communication and technology.












